description: The Solactive Swiss Large Cap Index (NTR) aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Swiss blue chip companies 20 largest and most liquid companies Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Quarterly index review, largest component is capped at 32.5%, all others at 17.5% Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.solactive.com
